message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "rule-audit: Static prompt audit for LLM system prompts"
abstract: "rule-audit is a static-analysis CLI for the AI reliability layer that audits LLM system prompts for silent failure modes — logical contradictions, coverage gaps, priority ambiguities, meta-rule paradoxes, and absoluteness issues — deterministically and offline, with no LLM calls and no network access."
type: software
